elements.name: Search the used car with model

steps.name: I am on homepage
I mouse hover on “buy+sell” tab
I click ‘Used’ link
I navigate to ‘Used Cars For Sale’ page
I select make "Audi" on used card search
I select model "A3" on used card search
I select location "NSW - All" on used card search
I select price "$30,000" on used card search
I click on Find My Next Car tab on used card search
I should see the make "Audi" in results
